<body class="d-flex align-items-center py-4 bg-body-tertiary">
    <main class="form-signin w-100 m-auto">
        <form action="{{ URL_BASE ~ '/authentication.php' }}" method="post" name="form-siging" id="form-siging">
            <div class="text-center mb-3">
                <img class="mb-4" src="{{ URL_BASE ~ '/views/assets/images/favicon.ico' }}" alt="" width="72" height="57">
                <h1 class="h3 mb-3 fw-normal">Gerenciador de Tickets</h1>
                <small>Preencha os campos abaixo com suas informações de acesso e tenha uma experiência incrível no gerenciamento de suas atividades diária.</small>
            </div>

            <div class="form-floating">
                <input type="email" name="email" id="email" class="form-control" id="floatingInput" value="bruno@teste.com" placeholder="joao@example.com" required />
                <label for="floatingInput">E-mail</label>
            </div>
            <div class="form-floating">
                <input type="password" name="password" id="password" class="form-control" id="floatingPassword" value="1234" placeholder="Senha" required />
                <label for="floatingPassword">Senha</label>
            </div>

            {% if ERROR is defined %}
            <small class="text-center my-3 text-danger">{{ ERROR }}</small>
            {% endif %}

            <div class="form-check text-start my-3">
                <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" value="remember-me" id="flexCheckDefault">
                <label class="form-check-label" for="flexCheckDefault">
                    Manter-se conectado
                </label>
            </div>

            <button class="btn btn-primary w-100 py-2 mb-3" type="submit">ENTRAR</button>
            
            <small class="text-center">Sou novo por aqui?  <a href="#">Cadastre-se</a></small>
        </form>
    </main>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-C6RzsynM9kWDrMNeT87bh95OGNyZPhcTNXj1NW7RuBCsyN/o0jlpcV8Qyq46cDfL" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>

